Class SessionTaskManager

java.lang.Object
com.cab302.peerpractice.Model.Managers.SessionTaskManager
public class SessionTaskManager extends Object
Manages session tasks with proper validation and permission checks. Uses an ISessionTaskDAO for persistence (in-memory or DB).
